title: Dozz

title: List of races
description: This application will allow you to make your shopping lists, and on top of that a beautiful interface for you, my favorite users.

title: Check Boxes
description: The aim is to tick the boxes when you find a food item in the store. Once ticked, you can either delete it, or it will move to the bottom of the list.
